text.div:
BC Entity Logical Model

Root class for entities such as people, organizations, and devices that have a separately identifiable existence. CIMI Alignment: In CIMI V0.0.4, Entity was a subclass of Party. Party is part of CIMI's participation model, which is undergoing review and revision. Rather than introducing the complexity of the CIMI participation model, which has little relevance to breast cancer profiles and is undergoing revision anyway, the Party class has been omitted.
